# Styling Standards

## Design System Integration

### Color System
```typescript
// ✅ CORRECT: Use CSS variables for colors
bg-primary, text-primary-foreground
bg-secondary, text-secondary-foreground
bg-muted, text-muted-foreground
bg-accent, text-accent-foreground
bg-destructive, text-destructive-foreground
border-input, ring-ring

// Sidebar colors
bg-sidebar, text-sidebar-foreground
bg-sidebar-accent, text-sidebar-accent-foreground
border-sidebar-border
```

### Spacing System
```typescript
// ✅ CORRECT: Use consistent spacing patterns
gap-4, px-6, py-4, rounded-xl
gap-6, px-8, py-6, rounded-lg
gap-2, px-3, py-2, rounded-md
```

### Typography
```typescript
// ✅ CORRECT: Use consistent typography
text-sm, font-medium, leading-none
text-base, font-semibold, leading-normal
text-lg, font-bold, leading-tight
```

## Component Styling Patterns

### Required Styling Elements
```typescript
// ✅ CORRECT: Always include these patterns
className={cn(
  "base-styles",
  "focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-ring/50 focus-visible:ring-[3px]",
  "aria-invalid:ring-destructive/20 dark:aria-invalid:ring-destructive/40",
  "aria-invalid:border-destructive",
  className
)}
```

### Dark Mode Support
```typescript
// ✅ CORRECT: Always include dark mode variants
"bg-background text-foreground dark:bg-background dark:text-foreground"
"border-border dark:border-border"
"shadow-sm dark:shadow-sm"
```

### Responsive Design
```typescript
// ✅ CORRECT: Use responsive utilities
"flex flex-col md:flex-row"
"w-full md:w-auto"
"text-sm md:text-base"
```

## Animation & Transitions
```typescript
// ✅ CORRECT: Use consistent transitions
transition-shadow
transition-[color,box-shadow]
transition-all duration-200
```

## Shadow System
```typescript
// ✅ CORRECT: Use consistent shadows
shadow-xs
shadow-sm
shadow-md
```

## Accessibility Styling
```typescript
// ✅ CORRECT: Focus and validation styles
"focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-ring/50 focus-visible:ring-[3px]"
"aria-invalid:ring-destructive/20 dark:aria-invalid:ring-destructive/40"
"aria-invalid:border-destructive"
"disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50"
```

